title: Video: REID – Diptera
body:
Having made a name for themselves with videos for the likes of **Blackbird Blackbird**, **Mmoths** and **Beat Culture**, amongst others, **Feel Good Lost** have released their newest offering in the form of beautifully fitting visuals for [**REID’s**](http://iamreid.com/) _Diptera_. Showing **REID** himself performing the track, set to a background of crashing waves and blustery, idyllic cliffs, cavorting in time with the hypnotic track, it’s safe to say that it’s yet another success for both the musician and **Feel Good Lost**.

[Reid // Diptera](http://vimeo.com/37317843) from [Feel Good Lost](http://vimeo.com/feelgoodlost) on [Vimeo](http://vimeo.com).
